definitions.definition: ( Internet ) An online photo - and video -sharing social networking service, originally designed to mimic old-fashioned instant cameras .
examples: Megan has 53 posts, follows all her followers and has 41.7k followers on Instagram .
He posted a gym reel on Instagram .

main_definition: ( Internet ) An online photo - and video -sharing social networking service, originally designed to mimic old-fashioned instant cameras .

definitions.definition: A user's profile or account on this service.
examples: Have you seen her Instagram lately?
She's been blowing up my Instagram !

definitions.definition: A photograph or video shared on this service.
examples: I saw one of her Instagrams last week, but I haven't talked to her since then.

main_definition: A user's profile or account on this service.
secondary_definitions: A photograph or video shared on this service.
